metadata.name: Return Of The Pac
metadata.description:
As kids, computer games gave us a world to escape to. An adventure in a place that fuelled our imaginations. And a way of putting off homework!  
But as we get older, with more responsibilities, the time to escape to these childhood memories are not as often for most of us. Unless we look really hard, and let out imagination take control again. Then, we see that these memories are always with us. Like here, Pac Man trying to feed in Frankfurt, Germany. Through the power and playfulness of photography, our imaginations are always centre stage...

Artists: @ArtFromAbove (Cynthia) & @robwdawkins (Rob)
